message.body: Hey Shawn I'm sorry I didn't get back to you. I've been in a tortured mood and a little sick. I'm going to try to rearrange my perspective and get to work but I've been feeling paralyzed about a lot of things. Just let me know when you want to come over and I won't ignore your message this time
No problem. I'm petty much free now or tomorrow sometime works
Ok let's do tomorrow so I can bubble wrap your piece and have it ready
